  "_meta": {
    "purpose": "Peripheral blood smear (PBS) morphology -> related disorders. Keys are YOLO class names (snake_case) produced by the pbs detector. The vision service looks up each detected class here and attaches related disorders + significance to the report. Decision support only; a haematologist validates.",
